<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>96</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Min dang cheng cheng sangin,
 A hawih chungnung Lal Isu;
 Zinmang henkawl ei sut,
 En in van Lalchutphah ah,
 Vai a hawm zing hi.

[V2]
 Ginna'n galin dawn leng,
 Nawpna pak leh A lungsietna zam velah,
 Lungdeih laituol a leng ding um?

[V3]
 2. Aw ka lautha lamvai,
 Na Lalpa mu lo na him?
 En in, Zion chaten,
 Kumsawt gam lopi zuonin,
 Pheiphung a suon ui.

[V4]
 3. Suol thimin gam lopi
 Leh ka Lalpa mel a lieh;
 Pielgal tuonglam ka vai,
 Thagau ei puiin lungngaih,
 Tui kinawk laiah.</lyrics>
<title>Min Dang Sangin !</title>
</song>